Karma is a versatile champion in League of Legends, who can support allies and deal damage to enemies.
Karma is often played as a support champion.
Karma's ultimate ability empowers her other abilities.
Karma's overall appearance is inspired by the concept of balance and harmony.
Karma's mantra in League of Legends is "the cycle of life and death continues, we will live, they will die."
Karma's passive ability in League of Legends grants her bonus movement speed when she damages enemy champions.
Karma's philosophy in League of Legends is based on the concept of karma, where actions have consequences that will eventually come back to the doer.